{"article_id":"nG1yl0A79UCvCdMi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republicans Reject Kavanaugh Accuser 's Request","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"To Delay Hearing For FBI Investigation","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee will move forward with a hearing","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"scheduled for Monday","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"on sexual assault allegations against Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"despite a request for further investigation from his accuser .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"The decision follows the release of a letter","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"sent to Senate Judiciary Commitee Chairman Chuck Grassley from attorneys","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"representing Christine Blasey Ford , the woman","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who accused Kavanaugh of sexually assaulting her more than three decades ago","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"when they were teenagers .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"In the letter , Ford 's attorneys said","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"an FBI investigation should be `` the first step","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"in addressing her allegations . ''","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Ford 's attorneys argue","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that an investigation is necessary","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"so that `` the Committee is fully informed","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"before conducting any hearing","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"or making any decisions . ''","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"Ford 's attorneys also say","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"since she went public with her allegations","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"`` she has been the target of vicious harassment and even death threats . ''","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"They also complained","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that the committee scheduled Ford to `` testify at the same table as Judge Kavanaugh in front of two dozen U.S . Senators on national television","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to relive this traumatic and harrowing incident . '' `` The invitation for Monday still stands , ''","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Grassley said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"`` Nothing","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"the FBI or any other investigator does","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"would have any bearing on what Dr. Ford tells the committee ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"so there is no reason for any further delay . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Grassley 's decision echoed the sentiment of Sen. Orrin Hatch , R-Utah , a former chairman of the Senate Judiciary Committee .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"`` The FBI does not do investigations like this .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"The responsibility falls to us , ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Hatch tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"`` We should proceed","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"as planned . ''","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"And retiring Sen. Bob Corker , R-Tenn. , suggested","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"if Ford did not appear at Monday 's hearing ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Senate Republicans should proceed to move forward","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"considering Kavanaugh 's nomination.","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"`` If we do n't hear from both sides on Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"let 's vote , ''","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Corker posted on Twitter late Tuesday night .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"The letter from Ford 's attorneys and Grassley 's response capped a day of uncertainty about the next step in the Kavanaugh confirmation process ,","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"which has spiraled into turmoil in recent days .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Ford 's attorneys stopped short of saying","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Ford will refuse to appear before the committee","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"while objecting to the rushed timeline and comments from Republican senators","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"who seemed to question her accusations .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"`` The hearing was scheduled for six short days from today","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"and would include interrogation by Senators","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"who appear to have made up their minds","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that she is 'mistaken ' and 'mixed up , ' ``","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the letter reads .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"`` While no sexual assault survivor should be subjected to such an ordeal ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Dr. Ford wants to cooperate with the Committee and with law enforcement officials . ''","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"including Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"issued statements","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"supporting Ford 's concerns about the hearing .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"`` I strongly support Dr. Ford 's call for an FBI investigation","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"before a hearing is held , ''","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"`` Dr. Ford 's call","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"for the FBI to investigate","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"also demonstrates her confidence","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"when all the facts are examined by an impartial investigation ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"her account will be further corroborated and confirmed . ''","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"California Sen. Dianne Feinstein , the top Democrat on the Judiciary Committee , also weighed in","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"to support Ford .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"`` We should honor Dr. Blasey Ford 's wishes","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and delay this hearing , ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Feinstein said in a statment .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"`` A proper investigation must be completed ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"witnesses interviewed ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"evidence reviewed","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"and all sides spoken to .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Only then should the chairman set a hearing date . ''","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Earlier in the day , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , said","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"the Senate Judiciary Committee would offer Ford the opportunity","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"to testify in either an open public session or behind closed doors about her allegation .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"`` She could do it privately","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"if she prefers ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"or publicly","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"if she prefers , ''","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"McConnell said ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"`` Monday is her opportunity . ''","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"He stressed","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"that Kavanaugh is eager to provide his testimony .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Democratic aides have privately floated the possibility","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"of boycotting the hearing","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"if Republicans choose to proceed","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"without Ford present .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Grassley 's committee staff has already begun conducting preliminary interviews by phone with alleged witnesses","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"related to the incident","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that Ford described to the Washington Post as having happened in the early 1980s","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"when she and Kavanaugh were teenagers","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"living in the Washington , D.C. , suburbs .","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"Aides plan follow-up sessions","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"as needed","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"to obtain additional information ahead of Monday 's planned public hearing .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Ford named Mark Judge , a classmate of Kavanaugh 's , as a witness to the incident at the high school party ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"but Judge told the Weekly Standard earlier this week","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"he does n't recall the episode .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Grassley 's office released a letter from Judge 's attorney on Tuesday with a statement from him","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"he has `` no memory '' of the incident .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"He also says ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"`` I have no more information","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"to offer the Committee","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"and I do not wish to speak publicly regarding the incidents","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"described in Dr. Ford 's letter . ''","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"Democrats have rejected the GOP process","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"and are refusing to participate in any committee phone interviews .","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"They are insisting","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"that the hearing be delayed","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"to further explore the allegations .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"They want additional witnesses beyond Kavanaugh and Ford to be added to the planned hearing Monday .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"But their primary demand is one","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"that Ford asked for her in her letter Tuesday night -","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"that the FBI conduct a full evaluation","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"before any hearing is held .","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"That 's a proposal","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"President Trump himself rejected earlier Tuesday prior to the release of the letter from Ford 's attorneys .","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"`` That 's not what they do , ''","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"Trump said .","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"`` They have done now , supposedly , six background checks","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"as Judge Kavanaugh has gone beautifully up a ladder . ''","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"On Monday a spokesperson for the Justice Department indicated","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that the FBI does not get involved in matters","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"unless a federal crime is alleged","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and that it had completed its work","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"related to Kavanaugh 's background check .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Speaking at a joint news conference with Polish President Andrzej Sebastian Duda ,","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"Trump said Tuesday","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"he feels `` so badly ''","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"that Kavanaugh is going through the ordeal of the accusations .","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"`` I feel terribly for him , for his wife and for his beautiful young daughters , ''","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"Trump said .","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"`` I feel terribly for them . ''","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"Washington state Sen. Patty Murray , the No . 3 Democrat in the Senate , told reporters","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"that an FBI investigation is necessary","depth":17},{"id":147,"text":"to ensure a full and impartial assessment of the accusations .","depth":17},{"id":148,"text":"`` Scheduling a hearing for Monday , a week from when Dr. Ford made her accusations public , is a shameful attempt","depth":19},{"id":149,"text":"to jam this through","depth":19},{"id":150,"text":"without giving anyone the time","depth":19},{"id":151,"text":"they need to investigate","depth":20},{"id":152,"text":"and put together the questions","depth":21},{"id":153,"text":"that need to be asked , ''","depth":21},{"id":154,"text":"Murray said .","depth":17},{"id":155,"text":"`` This is a test for the United States Senate","depth":17},{"id":156,"text":"on how we handle accusations of sexual harassment and assault . ''","depth":17},{"id":157,"text":"Murray and other Democrats are drawing a direct parallel between the claims against Kavanaugh and those","depth":17},{"id":158,"text":"raised in 1991","depth":18},{"id":159,"text":"when Anita Hill accused Clarence Thomas of sexual harassment during his confirmation hearings for the Supreme Court .","depth":18},{"id":160,"text":"At the time an all-male Senate Judiciary Committee aggressively questioned Hill in televised hearings ,","depth":17},{"id":161,"text":"cast doubt on her accusations","depth":18},{"id":162,"text":"and ultimately voted to move Thomas ' nomination to the full Senate","depth":19},{"id":163,"text":"which confirmed him to the court .","depth":19},{"id":164,"text":"That incident inspired a record number of women to run for federal office that cycle ,","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"including Murray ,","depth":17},{"id":166,"text":"who was elected the following year .","depth":17},{"id":167,"text":"Murray told reporters","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"America - and women in particular -","depth":16},{"id":169,"text":"will be closely watching how Ford 's case is handled .","depth":16},{"id":170,"text":"`` If Republicans attack Dr. Ford","depth":18},{"id":171,"text":"and this turns into anything like what we saw in 1991 ,","depth":18},{"id":172,"text":"women across the country are going to rise up","depth":19},{"id":173,"text":"and make their voice heard","depth":19},{"id":174,"text":"and Republicans will pay a very huge price , ''","depth":18},{"id":175,"text":"Murray said .","depth":16},{"id":176,"text":"`` I am here today","depth":17},{"id":177,"text":"to say ,","depth":17},{"id":178,"text":"once again , women are watching ,","depth":17},{"id":179,"text":"we are not going allow that to happen again . ''","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"Before Ford asked for an FBI investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"McConnell and other leaders said","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"they wanted to hear directly from Ford","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"but were standing firm on their expectation","depth":17},{"id":184,"text":"that she appear before the committee on Monday ,","depth":17},{"id":185,"text":"blaming Democrats for creating a disorderly examination of Kavanaugh 's record .","depth":16},{"id":186,"text":"`` Next week Dr. Ford and Judge Kavanaugh will testify to the Senate Judiciary Committee under oath , ''","depth":15},{"id":187,"text":"McConnell said Tuesday .","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"`` We should not have gotten to this point .","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"That this process has played out with so little order and so little sensitivity lies solely at the feet of Senate Democrats . ''","depth":15},{"id":190,"text":"Republicans have accused Feinstein of concealing details of Ford 's accusation","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"for several months","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"after it was sent to her office in July .","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"Feinstein referred the information to the FBI","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"but did not discuss it","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"until Ford went public over the weekend .","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"She defended her decision","depth":15},{"id":197,"text":"to keep the letter private","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"Tuesday ,","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"she was respecting Ford 's own request for anonymity","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"and following procedure","depth":16},{"id":202,"text":"for working with federal investigators .","depth":16},{"id":203,"text":"`` What we were trying to do was get an investigation , ''","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"Feinstein said .","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"`` We were going through all of that process . ''","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"Some Republicans are warning","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"that the Judiciary Committee has to tread lightly","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"and handle the accusations with respect ,","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"regardless of their timing .","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"Retiring Sen. Jeff Flake , R-Ariz. , told reporters","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"that there is a risk","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"in being too aggressive or appearing to bully Ford .","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"McConnell and other top GOP leaders repeatedly stressed","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"that Ford deserved to be heard","depth":14},{"id":215,"text":"and they hoped","depth":14},{"id":216,"text":"she would agree to testify .","depth":14},{"id":217,"text":"Maine Sen. Susan Collins ,","depth":15},{"id":218,"text":"who is one of just a handful of Republicans","depth":16},{"id":219,"text":"who have not said","depth":17},{"id":220,"text":"whether they plan to support Kavanaugh ,","depth":17},{"id":221,"text":"proposed calling both Kavanaugh and Ford to testify","depth":15},{"id":222,"text":"and allowing their attorneys to question them both as witnesses .","depth":15},{"id":223,"text":"`` I believe","depth":15},{"id":224,"text":"that would elicit the most information , ''","depth":15},{"id":225,"text":"Collins said .","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":451,"left":227,"right":450,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":227,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":450,"left":270,"right":449,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":230,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":229,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":228,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":254,"right":268,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":234,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":6,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":7,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":8,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":245,"right":252,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":241,"right":244,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":241,"left":236,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":11,"right":235,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":235,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":14,"right":239,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":15,"right":238,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":16,"right":237,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":19,"right":243,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":20,"right":242,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":242,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":23,"right":251,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":247,"right":250,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":246,"right":26,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":249,"right":30,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":248,"right":29,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":248,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":260,"right":267,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":31,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":256,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":255,"right":34,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":35,"right":257,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":257,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":264,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":38,"right":263,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":39,"right":262,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":40,"right":261,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":261,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":45,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":449,"left":282,"right":448,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":271,"right":281,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":274,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":272,"right":273,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":278,"right":279,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":52,"right":277,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":277,"left":276,"right":56,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":53,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":279,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":448,"left":304,"right":447,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":304,"left":294,"right":303,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":285,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":283,"right":284,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":287,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},